{"tid":637693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇見個fd啲廢青生活真係嬲","createTime":"2018-04-22T05:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T06:57:28.000Z","uid":77235,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b16e5c0c4552cb72e34311bed167e7ec6e73878","tid":637693,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"個fd屋企人18歲就買左層樓比佢拍拖結婚<br />\n但佢自從做過一次兵之後就唔敢識女仔<br />\n依家食住就痴屋企 層樓就拎去放租供股票<br />\n然後日日就係屋企打機睇動漫 工又唔番街又唔出旅行又唔去又唔搵野學下<br />\n都唔知佢做人為咩<br />\n最嬲既係我好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70678f3bf62e26bfd01a52153899479978a7ccb1","tid":637693,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁似我之前啲生活嘅"},{"pid":"6256c0e0a1d1eb62c7755515ea1943cd9310728f","tid":637693,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"咁樓主做人為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a146ed50df93c2aa6eaf90c630fdb80c08997f83","tid":637693,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"咁似我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我有番工同半年一次旅行"},{"pid":"244fcf461722f38d1d8524f618751022ec1b8c96","tid":637693,"uid":139139,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"今年去咗七次旅行<br />\n台北大阪菲律賓柬埔寨多倫多古巴東京<br />\n全部都係老母俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔俾我留係屋企打機<br />\n<br />\n所以每次去旅行我都好唔開心"},{"pid":"6e52bb75dedddeaf5a6af5bb47d8bcc05c5c0c39","tid":637693,"uid":2795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"244fcf461722f38d1d8524f618751022ec1b8c96","tid":637693,"uid":139139,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"今年去咗七次旅行<br />\n台